# codex-os-managed
# gate_id|required|owner|threshold|command|env_var(optional)
preflight|true|release|required files, scripts, baselines, and CSP are valid|pnpm preflight

git_hygiene|true|qa|all git safety guards pass|pnpm git:guard:all

typecheck_ts|true|qa|TypeScript noEmit passes|pnpm typecheck
rust_tests|true|qa|Rust library tests pass|pnpm test:rust
rust_lint|true|qa|Rust clippy runs with -D warnings|pnpm lint:rust
ui_smoke|true|qa|Browser smoke flow passes|pnpm test:e2e

perf_bundle|true|performance|bundle metrics captured|pnpm perf:bundle
perf_build|true|performance|build-time metrics captured|pnpm perf:build
perf_assets|true|performance|asset budgets pass|pnpm perf:assets
perf_memory|true|performance|memory budgets pass|pnpm perf:memory
perf_summary|true|performance|summary generated|pnpm perf:summary
perf_complete|true|performance|required perf gates are not-run free|pnpm perf:assert-complete
